{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-modules-jsx","path":"/modules/machines","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"machines\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#machines\" aria-label=\"machines permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Machines</h2>\n<p>A module that provides the infrastructure to easily make machines for processing or assembly of materials.</p>\n<p>See the forum for discussion: <a href=\"http://forum.terasology.org/threads/machines.938/\">http://forum.terasology.org/threads/machines.938/</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"entity-network\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#entity-network\" aria-label=\"entity network permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Entity Network</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A set of components and systems to join entities together in a group.  These groups can then be queried so that interactions between joined entites can be orchestrated.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"src/main/java/org/terasology/entityNetwork/README.md\">Entity Network Readme</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"fluid\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fluid\" aria-label=\"fluid permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fluid</h2>\n<p>see Fluid</p>\n<h2 id=\"fluid-transport\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fluid-transport\" aria-label=\"fluid transport permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fluid Transport</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Tanks that can be interacted with by containers of fluid (like a bucket).</li>\n<li>Pipes that simulate gravity and let fluid naturally flow from elevated tanks to lower tanks.</li>\n<li>Pumps that input power to lift fluid to elevated tanks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"item-transport\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#item-transport\" aria-label=\"item transport permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Item Transport</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ejection/extraction of items to/from adjacent inventories</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"machines-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#machines-1\" aria-label=\"machines 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Machines</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A default UI implementation for an inventory based workstation process that allows a single visual extension</li>\n<li>A system to simplify setup of a block to be a machine. It will automatically add an inventory, slot mappings, and extension of the default UI</li>\n<li>Surface Placement block family to assist connecting devices in the right direction</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"mechanical-power\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mechanical-power\" aria-label=\"mechanical power permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mechanical Power</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Uses the EntityNetwork submodule and PotentialEnergyDevices module to enable transfer, storage, and production of energy</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"src/main/java/org/terasology/mechanicalPower/README.md\">Mechanical Power Readme</a></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Machines A module that provides the infrastructure to easily make machines for processing or assembly of materials. See the forum forâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Machines","cover":{"publicURL":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/cover.png","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/9e1f0/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/8dfb2/cover.jpg 480w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/2f986/cover.jpg 960w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/9e1f0/cover.jpg 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/3fa69/cover.webp 480w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/986c9/cover.webp 960w,\n/ModuleSite/static/528951686128b0b0eeff76c8479748d7/34dc0/cover.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":1000}}},"date":null,"tags":["Library"]},"fields":{"slug":"/machines","date":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/machines"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1865044719"]}